{"word":"G601 - ἀποκαλύπτω - apokalýptō - ap-ok-al-oop'-to - Reveal","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποκαλύπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apokalýptō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-ok-al-oop'-to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Reveal</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வெளிப்படுத்து"},{"paragraph":"to uncover, lay open what has been veiled or covered up; to disclose, make bare"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G2572 - καλύπτω - kalýptō - kal-oop'-to/2572\">G2572</a>; to take <i>off the cover</i>, that is, <i>disclose:</i> - reveal.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2571/2571\">G2571</a>, <a href=\"#/G2572/2572\">G2572</a>, <a href=\"#/G2619/2619\">G2619</a>, <a href=\"#/G343/343\">G343</a>, <a href=\"#/G601/601\">G601</a>, <a href=\"#/G602/602\">G602</a>"}]}